From 88ebf49515c69e47f0e7e02d3fa7b5d5862b2385 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Namjae Jeon <linkinjeon@kernel.org>
Date: Fri, 13 Feb 2026 10:40:41 +0900
Subject: [PATCH 07/43] ntfs: update directory operations

Update the directory and index operations to support full read-write
functionality and use the folio API, including directory modification.

Acked-by: Christoph Hellwig <hch@lst.de>
Reviewed-by: Christoph Hellwig <hch@lst.de>
Signed-off-by: Namjae Jeon <linkinjeon@kernel.org>
